      "description": "[Meticulous.ai](https://www.meticulous.ai/) captures the natural testing sessions (on localhost, preview URLs and staging stacks) that you're already doing while developing your application. It analyses which lines in the codebase each flow tests, and from this curates an ever evolving set of visual end-to-end tests designed to cover every distinct line of codebase. These tests test all logical, behavioral and visual changes.\r\n\r\nCover your app's 1000s of edge cases, with no need to write or maintain tests. As your app evolves so does the test suite.\r\n\r\nRead more at https://meticulous.ai/",
